summary: Star of the show Phil and sarcastic stagehand Dan both love musicals. But with Phil being the Disney prince of people’s dreams...
caption:
Star of the show Phil and sarcastic stagehand Dan both love musicals. But with Phil being the Disney prince of people’s dreams and Dan with the aesthetic of J.D., they both argue quite often, to the disdain of the school, about whether broadway or disney truly makes the best musicals. anger leads to hate, hate leads to suffering, and suffering leads to a friendship no one saw coming.


aye so this is my submission for @dyxnamic-art ‘s contrast challenge. This idea literally came to me at midnight a while back so it might be a bit random welp but you know thats how it is.

also loosly based of thomas sander’s video, The Dark Side of Disney. Thats where the quotes from anyways

ok thats it bye
